            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Atto habitator in Colonia"
                            >Ato</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Eugenius"
                                >Augeni</name></persName> habitator in <placeName ref="#places/1001"
                            >Colonia</placeName>, quia in proprio territurio meo <rs key="#Churches"
                            >eclesiam</rs> in honore <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Monasteries #Private_foundations #Joint_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/600">sancti Michaeli archangeli</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Private_foundations">edificavi</rs>, et a domno <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/343">Peredeus</persName> in Dei nomine <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Joint_foundations">edificatum est</rs> in ipso loco <placeName
                            key="#Salae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Acorns #Churches #Monasteries #Private_foundations #Joint_foundations"
                            ref="#places/1001">Colonia</placeName>. <foreign>Ora offre</foreign> Deo
                        et tibi beatissimo sancti Mihaeli archangelo vel a tuo <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> a me constructo sexta portione ex
                        omnibus rebus meis, tam <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">silvis, virgariis</rs>,
                        cultum vel incultum, cum edificiis qui ante ipsa eclesia edificata esse
                        videtor, cum curte qui ante ipsa <rs key="#Salae">sala</rs> est. Ipsa sala
                        cum suprascripta curte in integro (…) cum sexta portione (…) ex omnibus
                        rebus meis. <foreign>I beni saranno gestiti dal prete che lui nominerà.
                            Obbligo di preghiere per lui e di luminaria. Si riserva l’usufrutto
                            vitalizio dei beni (insieme al rettore della chiesa). Vuole
                            anche</foreign> quis de redibus meis in ipso monasterio capite tonso,
                        caste vivendo, Deo deservire voluerit, ut potestatem habeat in ipso
                        monasterio vel ipsa res usufructuare, et dominum esset in omnibus.
                            <foreign>Altrimenti riserva agli eredi solo il diritto di
                            ordinatione</foreign> faciendo quomuniter vel ipso monasterio vel eius
                        res deferendo. (…) Actum in <placeName ref="#places/1001" key="#Vici"><rs
                                key="#Vici">vico</rs> Colonia</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Ati; + <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Richipertus">Rigiperti</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Maginpertus">Magniperti</name></persName>
                        testis; + <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Sigebertus"
                            >Seiperti</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Ursus"
                                >Ursi</name></persName> testis; + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gundipertus">Gudiperti</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gundualdus">Gudualdi</name></persName> testis;
                        + <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                            >Teiperti</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Aufridus"
                                >Aufrid</name></persName> testis; + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Felicissimus">Felicissimi</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gausmar">Gaudimari</name></persName> testis.
                            <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer #Priests"><name
                                ref="Fratellus">Fratellus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
